name: I know what you did RGB ❤️💚💙
description:
So.... unfortunate events led to some chaos in the latest mints, chaos must be induced to prevent love being collected by a single entity. 

The hens were all witnesses of what happened, they know what you did. 
Love is to be shared, now that you have so much love, you must start to think like a giver, and give, share, distribute to as many other entities. Or be remembered as the sick one who also burned the hens. You don't want to burn hen alive don't you? Of course you are not that kind of person.
